            <p>
                Using Azure AI Speech, our platform will be able to accurately scan assessments questions from digital papers thanks to its text-to-speech technology.
                Through seamless integration with tactile interfaces and screen readers,
                the system vocalizes the questions instantaneously, making it possible for students with visual difficulties to access and comprehend with ease.
            </p>
